title: Marry Me
overview: Marry Me is a romantic comedy miniseries. Rae Ann Carter is an artist turned social worker who is looking for the right man to marry. Just as she thinks she has one in Adam, both she and Adam break up. Unsure, she tries again with Luke, who wants to be the right one: then another man, Harry, takes an interest in her followed by Adam's return. With three men buzzing around her like bees, Rae Ann has a decision to make.
